Articles

An article is any 'article of content'. Articles can have sections and those sections can contain other articles. Just go with it, it's better than what we had.

This is an article within an article, so I gave it a class of address-example and put a broder around it using the CSS, so that you can see the extent of the inner article.



Asides

An aside is an element of content that is presented alongside the main content.

This means that there is more flexibility about where it gets displayed, depending on the browsing context.
This is an aside. By the way, you're doing great.
